      <title>监管机构警告称，爱尔兰必须在下一轮预算中表现出克制</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-05/ireland-must-show-restraint-in-next-budget-watchdog-warns</link>
      <description><![CDATA[爱尔兰财政监管机构警告称，爱尔兰政府在制定下一份预算时需要保持克制，否则将面临经济过热的风险。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-05/ireland-must-show-restraint-in-next-budget-watchdog-warns</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 05 Jun 2024 05:45:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
